---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Dr. Todd Allen - Allen Psychiatry"
  description="About Dr. Todd Allen, DNP, PMHNP-BC - Allen Psychiatry, Provo, UT. Learn about Dr. Allen's background, philosophy, and commitment to mental health care."
>
  <Header />
  <!-- About Content Section -->
  <section class="about-content about-portrait-layout">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-flex">
        <div class="about-portrait">
          <img src="/images/todd-allen.jpg" alt="Dr. Todd Allen portrait" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-details">
          <h1>Dr. Todd Allen, DNP, PMHNP-BC</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Board Certified Psychiatric Mental Health Nurse Practitioner<br
            />Serving Provo, Utah County, and Rural Utah
          </p>
          <h2>Professional Background</h2>
          <p>
            Dr. Todd Allen, DNP, is a Board Certified Psychiatric Mental Health
            Nurse Practitioner (PMHNP-BC) serving Provo, UT, and the broader
            Utah County area, including rural communities that often face
            limited access to specialized mental health care. With his Doctor of
            Nursing Practice specializing in psychiatry, Dr. Allen brings
            advanced clinical expertise to individuals ages 14 to 55, with a
            primary focus on ADHD treatment in adolescents and adults. He also
            provides comprehensive care for depression, anxiety, PTSD, and the
            list goes on.
          </p>
          <h2>Research and Academic Contributions</h2>
          <p>
            His commitment to advancing psychiatric care extends beyond clinical
            practice through his sleep-study research and his role as a member
            of the research team with Boeson, contributing to innovative
            approaches in mental health treatment.
          </p>
          <h2>Community Focus and Understanding</h2>
          <p>
            Throughout his distinguished career, Dr. Allen has observed the
            far-reaching effects of mental health conditions on individuals,
            families, and communities across Utah County, particularly in
            underserved rural areas where specialized mental health care,
            including ADHD treatment, is difficult, inconvenient, with long
            distances needing to be traveled or often unavailable. This
            understanding drives his dedication to creating accessible,
            therapeutic environments where residents of both more urban areas of
            Utah County and surrounding rural communities, like Vernal and
            Richfield, can find support and evidence-based treatment.
          </p>
          <h2>Treatment Philosophy</h2>
          <p>
            He emphasizes strong therapeutic partnerships with each client,
            believing that authentic compassion and active listening form the
            foundation of effective mental health care, especially for those
            managing ADHD and related conditions.
          </p>
          <p>
            Dr. Allen integrates the latest evidence-based practices in ADHD
            treatment while staying current with emerging developments in
            psychiatric care, ensuring his patients receive comprehensive,
            holistic treatment options tailored to their unique needs.
          </p>
          <h2>Community Advocacy and Personal Connection</h2>
          <p>
            Beyond his clinical expertise, he understands the persistent stigma
            surrounding mental health treatment. He is passionate about
            educating communities on the vital importance of mental health care
            and how transformative quality treatment can be for individuals and
            families. Having grown up in rural communities himself, Dr. Allen
            holds deep respect for the resilience, hard work, and strong values
            found in these areas, and he is committed to bringing specialized
            ADHD care to those who may have previously lacked access to such
            services.
          </p>
          <h2>Patient Care Commitment</h2>
          <p>
            Dr. Allen is honored to support your mental health journey,
            providing a welcoming, non-judgmental space where you can feel
            heard, understood, and empowered to achieve lasting positive change.
          </p>
          <h2>Contact Information</h2>
          <p>
            Please call <a href="tel:3855041334">385-504-1334</a> to schedule your
            appointment today.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
